DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    TREATAS({"Germany"}, 'Sales'[Country])

  VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Calendar'[Date])),
      'Calendar'[Date] >= DATE(2014, 1, 1)
    )

EVALUATE
  SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
    __DS0FilterTable,
    __DS0FilterTable2,
    "SumSalesAmount", IGNORE(CALCULATE(SUM('Sales'[SalesAmount])))
  )

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Calendar'[Date])),
      'Calendar'[Date] >= DATE(2014, 1, 1)
    )

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('Sales'[Category], "IsGrandTotalRowTotal", 'Sales'[SubCategory], "IsDM1Total"),
      __DS0FilterTable,
      "SumSalesAmount", CALCULATE(SUM('Sales'[SalesAmount])),
      "SumUnits", CALCULATE(SUM('Sales'[Units]))
    )

  VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM1 = 
    SELECTCOLUMNS(
      KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsDM1Total] = TRUE)),
      "IsGrandTotalRowTotal", [IsGrandTotalRowTotal],
      "'Sales'[Category]", 'Sales'[Category],
      "SortBy_DM1_0", [SumSalesAmount]
    )

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
    NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
      __DS0Core,
      __DS0CoreTableByDM1
    )

  VAR __DS0CoreNoInstanceFiltersNoTotals = 
    FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), AND([IsGrandTotalRowTotal] = FALSE, [IsDM1Total] = FALSE))

EVALUATE
  GROUPBY(
    __DS0CoreNoInstanceFiltersNoTotals,
    "MinSumSalesAmount", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [SumSalesAmount]),
    "MaxSumSalesAmount", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [SumSalesAmount]),
    "MinSumUnits", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [SumUnits]),
    "MaxSumUnits", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [SumUnits])
  )

EVALUATE
  TOPN(
    502,
    __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns,
    [IsGrandTotalRowTotal],
    0,
    [SortBy_DM1_0],
    0,
    'Sales'[Category],
    1,
    [IsDM1Total],
    0,
    [SumSalesAmount],
    0,
    'Sales'[SubCategory],
    1
  )

ORDER BY
  [IsGrandTotalRowTotal] DESC,
  [SortBy_DM1_0] DESC,
  'Sales'[Category],
  [IsDM1Total] DESC,
  [SumSalesAmount] DESC,
  'Sales'[SubCategory]

DEFINE VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
  FILTER(
    KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Calendar'[Date])),
    'Calendar'[Date] >= DATE(2014, 1, 1)
  )

EVALUATE
  TOPN(
    1002,
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'Sales'[Custom],
      __DS0FilterTable,
      "SumSalesAmount", CALCULATE(SUM('Sales'[SalesAmount]))
    ),
    'Sales'[Custom],
    1
  )

ORDER BY
  'Sales'[Custom]

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Calendar'[Date])),
      'Calendar'[Date] >= DATE(2014, 1, 1)
    )

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'Sales'[Class],
      ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('Sales'[Custom], "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"),
      __DS0FilterTable,
      "SumSalesAmount", CALCULATE(SUM('Sales'[SalesAmount])),
      "SumUnits", CALCULATE(SUM('Sales'[Units]))
    )

  VAR __DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals = 
    SELECTCOLUMNS(
      KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = FALSE)),
      "'Sales'[Class]", 'Sales'[Class],
      "'Sales'[Custom]", 'Sales'[Custom],
      "SumSalesAmount", [SumSalesAmount],
      "SumUnits", [SumUnits]
    )

  VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM0 = 
    SELECTCOLUMNS(
      KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = TRUE)),
      "'Sales'[Class]", 'Sales'[Class],
      "SortBy_DM0_0", [SumSalesAmount]
    )

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
    NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
      SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Sales'[Class]),
      __DS0CoreTableByDM0
    )

  VAR __DS0Primary = 
    TOPN(201, __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns, [SortBy_DM0_0], 1, 'Sales'[Class], 1)

  VAR __DS0Secondary = 
    TOPN(62, SUMMARIZE(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals, 'Sales'[Custom]), 'Sales'[Custom], 1)

EVALUATE
  __DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
  'Sales'[Custom]

EVALUATE
  NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
    __DS0Primary,
    SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
      __DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals,
      "ColumnIndex",
      __DS0Secondary,
      'Sales'[Custom],
      ASC
    )
  )

ORDER BY
  [SortBy_DM0_0], 'Sales'[Class], [ColumnIndex]

metrics.visualTitle: Sales, %GT Sales and Units by Year and Month

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Calendar'[Date])),
      'Calendar'[Date] >= DATE(2014, 1, 1)
    )

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'Calendar'[Year],
      'Calendar'[Month],
      'Calendar'[MonthN],
      __DS0FilterTable,
      "SumSalesAmount", CALCULATE(SUM('Sales'[SalesAmount])),
      "SumUnits", IGNORE(CALCULATE(SUM('Sales'[Units]))),
      "M2", CALCULATE(
        DIVIDE(SUM('Sales'[SalesAmount]), CALCULATE(
          SUM('Sales'[SalesAmount]),
          ALLSELECTED('Calendar'[Year]),
          ALLSELECTED('Calendar'[Month]),
          ALLSELECTED('Calendar'[MonthN])
        ))
      )
    )

EVALUATE
  GROUPBY(
    __DS0Core,
    "MinSumUnits", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [SumUnits]),
    "MaxSumUnits", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [SumUnits])
  )

EVALUATE
  TOPN(201, __DS0Core, 'Calendar'[Year], 1, 'Calendar'[MonthN], 1, 'Calendar'[Month], 1)

ORDER BY
  'Calendar'[Year], 'Calendar'[MonthN], 'Calendar'[Month]
